      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰派遣军队阻止俄罗斯在哈尔科夫地区的前进</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/ukraine-sends-forces-to-halt-russia-s-advance-in-kharkiv-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在俄罗斯自2022年以来首次对哈尔科夫地区发动大规模攻势后，乌克兰正在部署更多部队以稳定其东北前线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/ukraine-sends-forces-to-halt-russia-s-advance-in-kharkiv-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 08:54:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾将调查外国外交官在中国威胁后的行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/philippines-to-probe-foreign-diplomats-acts-after-china-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国威胁要公布所谓的南海协议通话录音后，菲律宾外交部表示将“调查任何有关外国外交官非法活动的报道”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/philippines-to-probe-foreign-diplomats-acts-after-china-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 08:06:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国指控三项与香港有关的安全犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/uk-charges-three-over-hong-kong-related-security-offences</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在伦敦警察厅反恐部队进行调查后，英国指控三名男子协助香港外国情报部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/uk-charges-three-over-hong-kong-related-security-offences</guid>
